Teresa L. SLADEK, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
EMPLOYMENT APPEAL BOARD and Kelly Services USA LLC, Defendants-Appellees. No. 18-0981 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 15, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Teresa Sladek appeals the denial of her application for unemployment benefits. AFFIRMED.
